Type species. 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:7CE765F5-571B-4CA9-9C77-29A55E3509C6" authority="Cuvier, 1830" authorityName="Cuvier" authorityYear="1830" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sciaenidae" genus="Micropogon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Micropogon trifilis Müller &amp; Troschel 1849:622" order="Perciformes" pageNumber="2" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="trifilis">
Micropogon trifilis 
